<body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" tts:textAlign="center">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:18.128" end="00:00:22.384">Ett, tv&#229;. Ett, tv&#229;, tre, fyr</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22.514" end="00:00:23.433"/>
      <p begin="00:00:23.558" end="00:00:25.665">Om du tycker om James Browns musik </p>
      <p begin="00:00:25.665" end="00:00:27.557">kommer du ha riktigt roligt ikv&#228;ll.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:27.557" end="00:00:29.731">Ikv&#228;ll firar vi Black Velvet,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:29.731" end="00:00:33.816">James Brown Jr.'s 62:a f&#246;delsedag</p>
      <p begin="00:00:33.818" end="00:00:36.405" region="top"> Whoo, 62!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:36.435" end="00:00:38.463" region="top"> S&#229; ge en varm appl&#229;d</p>
      <p begin="00:00:38.487" end="00:00:39.718" region="top"> till den h&#228;r unge mannen</p>
      <p begin="00:00:39.718" end="00:00:41.503" region="top"> som &#228;r p&#229; v&#228;g upp p&#229; scenen</p>
      <p begin="00:00:41.503" end="00:00:43.646">Han har varit p&#229; David Letterman Show,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43.646" end="00:00:45.731">H&#228;lsa honom v&#228;lkommen med en stor appl&#229;d</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45.731" end="00:00:49.913">Black Velvet, James Brown, Jr!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49.913" end="00:00:52.226"/>
      <p begin="00:00:52.226" end="00:00:53.898"/>
      <p begin="00:00:53.898" end="00:00:59.189">&#9834; Det &#228;r en mans v&#228;rld. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.189" end="00:01:05.490">&#9834; Men den &#228;r inget, inget... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:01:05.490" end="00:01:06.648">- Jag har spelat James Brown</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06.648" end="00:01:13.882">sen jag var 14 &#229;r gammal.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:13.882" end="00:01:16.398"/>
      <p begin="00:01:16.398" end="00:01:17.857"/>
      <p begin="00:01:17.867" end="00:01:21.183"/>
      <p begin="00:01:21.183" end="00:01:25.769"/>
      <p begin="00:01:25.769" end="00:01:29.677">Men nu vill jag vara Charles Bradley.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:29.677" end="00:01:52.332"/>
      <p begin="00:01:52.486" end="00:01:54.356" region="top"> Min f&#246;rsta skiva med egna l&#229;tar</p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.356" end="00:01:58.013" region="top"> sl&#228;pps den 25:e januari.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.013" end="00:02:01.149">Jag har k&#228;mpat i &#246;ver 42 &#229;r</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.149" end="00:02:02.890">f&#246;r att lyckas i branschen</p>
      <p begin="00:02:02.890" end="00:02:04.606">och vid 62 &#229;rs &#229;lder</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.606" end="00:02:06.648">b&#246;rjar jag &#228;ntligen se en ljusning.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:08.956" end="00:02:10.939">Jag har aldrig tj&#228;nat nog med pengar</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.939" end="00:02:13.794">f&#246;r att f&#246;rs&#246;rja mig p&#229; musiken,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.794" end="00:02:15.857">men jag hoppas att den h&#228;r skivan</p>
      <p begin="00:02:15.857" end="00:02:17.304">ska bli en v&#228;ndpunkt</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.304" end="00:02:20.111">s&#229; att jag kan f&#246;rs&#246;rja mig p&#229; musiken.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.168" end="00:02:26.690">Du....</p>
      <p begin="00:02:26.690" end="00:02:28.659">Jag h&#228;mtar lite vatten &#229;t dig, OK?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.659" end="00:02:30.004">H&#246;rru.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.004" end="00:02:30.982">Det d&#228;r &#228;r min f&#229;gel.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.982" end="00:02:32.494">Den g&#246;r mig arg.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:32.494" end="00:02:33.628">N&#228;r jag blir arg g&#229;r jag d&#228;rifr&#229;n</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.628" end="00:02:35.364">till ett annat rum och st&#228;nger d&#246;rren,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35.364" end="00:02:37.170">l&#229;ter honom skrika s&#229; mycket han vill.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:37.861" end="00:02:38.897">Jag har mitt eget lilla st&#228;lle.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.897" end="00:02:40.429">Det &#228;r inte precis vad jag vill ha</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.429" end="00:02:43.035">men jag tackar Gud att jag har en bostad.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:44.056" end="00:02:45.363">N&#228;r jag g&#229;r in i min lilla l&#228;genhet</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.363" end="00:02:46.945">och l&#229;ser d&#246;rren</p>
      <p begin="00:02:46.945" end="00:02:48.565">k&#228;nner jag mig tillfreds.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:48.565" end="00:02:50.325">Men n&#228;r jag &#229;ker till ghettot,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:50.325" end="00:02:53.051">g&#229;r in i hissen,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:53.051" end="00:02:54.232">kommer dit,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:54.232" end="00:02:55.369">det &#228;r d&#229; problemen b&#246;rjar.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.369" end="00:02:56.898">Man vet aldrig</p>
      <p begin="00:02:56.898" end="00:02:58.994">vad som kan h&#228;nda d&#228;r inne.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:58.994" end="00:03:00.482">Vi kom ner</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.482" end="00:03:02.183">och s&#229;g Alfred.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.183" end="00:03:03.022">Bra kille, st&#246;rde aldrig n&#229;gon.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:03.022" end="00:03:04.598">En kyrkokille.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:04.598" end="00:03:06.544">De har skjutit in i hans l&#228;genhet.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.544" end="00:03:08.274">Han visade mig var de hade skjutit.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08.289" end="00:03:10.510">Jag sa: "Wow, man." Jag sa:</p>
      <p begin="00:03:10.550" end="00:03:12.823">"Jag vill inte bo p&#229; bottenv&#229;ningen."</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12.823" end="00:03:14.391">- N&#228;r det blir f&#246;r galet</p>
      <p begin="00:03:14.391" end="00:03:16.092">i ghettot</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16.092" end="00:03:17.808">&#229;ker jag till min mammas hus</p>
      <p begin="00:03:17.808" end="00:03:19.537">och sover i hennes k&#228;llare.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:31.862" end="00:03:33.477">- S&#229; jag kommer hit</p>
      <p begin="00:03:33.477" end="00:03:35.794">och det &#228;r h&#228;r jag sover.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:35.794" end="00:03:37.051">Tills n&#228;sta dag</p>
      <p begin="00:03:37.051" end="00:03:38.838">d&#229; jag tar hand om deras &#228;renden.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:38.838" end="00:03:39.884">Tar hand om allt som beh&#246;vs</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.884" end="00:03:43.414">f&#246;r att ha vi ska ha tak &#246;ver huvudet.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:43.707" end="00:03:47.142">- Jag tycker om att rulla ihop det h&#228;r</p>
      <p begin="00:03:47.142" end="00:03:48.735">till en liten boll.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:50.722" end="00:03:53.068">- Sl&#228;ng i dem h&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55.486" end="00:03:56.661">- Hur g&#229;r det med riset?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:56.829" end="00:03:58.127">- L&#229;t mig se?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:59.894" end="00:04:01.813">En liten stund till.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:01.951" end="00:04:04.880">- Vi var 8 personer i v&#229;r familj.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:04.942" end="00:04:07.772">Mitt huvudm&#229;l var att ta hand om</p>
      <p begin="00:04:07.772" end="00:04:11.547">min mamma s&#229; bra som m&#246;jligt.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.454" end="00:04:14.409" region="top"> - Han &#228;r min gullunge</p>
      <p begin="00:04:14.409" end="00:04:16.520" region="top"> och jag &#228;lskar honom.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.626" end="00:04:18.297" region="top"> Han tv&#228;ttar mina kl&#228;der.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:18.467" end="00:04:19.206" region="top"> Han st&#228;dar mitt hus.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.206" end="00:04:20.684" region="top"> P&#229; Alla hj&#228;rtans dag</p>
      <p begin="00:04:20.684" end="00:04:23.291" region="top"> kom han med en l&#229;da godis.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:23.291" end="00:04:24.646" region="top"> Han &#228;r lika s&#246;t</p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.646" end="00:04:25.871" region="top"> som godisl&#229;dan.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:25.871" end="00:04:27.567">- Jag vill bara</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.567" end="00:04:28.273">att hennes liv ska vara fridfullt</p>
      <p begin="00:04:28.273" end="00:04:29.398">s&#229; att</p>
      <p begin="00:04:29.398" end="00:04:31.440">hon slipper oroa sig f&#246;r r&#228;kningar</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.440" end="00:04:33.038">och s&#229;nt.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.038" end="00:04:34.203">- Jag tog p&#229; mig det ansvaret</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.203" end="00:04:35.913">men jag visste inte riktigt</p>
      <p begin="00:04:35.913" end="00:04:37.453">vad jag hade gett mig in p&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.453" end="00:04:38.414">Men nu har jag redan b&#246;rjat.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38.414" end="00:04:39.802">Jag kommer inte att &#228;ndra mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:39.802" end="00:04:40.970">S&#229; det enda jag kan g&#246;ra &#228;r</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.970" end="00:04:42.685">att f&#246;rs&#246;ka hitta ett s&#228;tt att f&#229;</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.685" end="00:04:44.012">en stadig inkomst</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.012" end="00:04:46.923">s&#229; jag kan klara mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:46.923" end="00:04:49.739">Mer &#228;n s&#229; kan jag inte beg&#228;ra just nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:56.578" end="00:05:00.314">&#9834; Runt och runt &#229;ker vi igen. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00.314" end="00:05:04.916">&#9834; Vart tar det v&#228;gen, ingen vet.. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:04.916" end="00:05:08.256">&#9834; Det &#228;r en kall kall v&#228;rld.&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.656" end="00:05:12.156">&#9834; Det &#228;r en kall kall v&#228;rld. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.939" end="00:05:15.856">&#9834; Hur kan vi stoppa f&#246;r&#228;ndringarna &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:15.856" end="00:05:20.897">&#9834; som sker i USA idag?&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:30.701" end="00:05:34.686">&#9834; Ohhh, ohhh, ohhh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.124" end="00:05:43.231">&#9834; Ta mig tillbaks. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.231" end="00:05:46.939">&#9834; Ta mig tillbaks till gyllene tiderna. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:46.939" end="00:05:48.645">&#9834; Oh. Ah. Uh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.105" end="00:05:50.612">&#9834; Ta mig tillbaka. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:50.612" end="00:05:55.148">&#9834; Tillbaka till de gyllene tiderna. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55.148" end="00:05:57.856">&#9834; Rasera allt. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:57.856" end="00:06:11.172"/>
      <p begin="00:06:11.192" end="00:06:13.064">- Det var en s&#229;ng</p>
      <p begin="00:06:13.064" end="00:06:15.023">fr&#229;n nya skivan "No Time For Dreaming."</p>
      <p begin="00:06:15.023" end="00:06:16.148">Charles Bradley</p>
      <p begin="00:06:16.148" end="00:06:17.274">and the Menahan Street Band.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17.274" end="00:06:18.731">- Jag kan inte fatta</p>
      <p begin="00:06:18.731" end="00:06:20.064">att du kom fr&#229;n ingenstans</p>
      <p begin="00:06:20.064" end="00:06:22.273">helt ok&#228;nd f&#246;r oss.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:22.273" end="00:06:24.473">- Har du spelat in f&#246;rut?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:24.596" end="00:06:25.890">- Nej.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:25.890" end="00:06:28.431">Det &#228;r min f&#246;rsta inspelning, som sl&#228;pps.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:28.431" end="00:06:29.958">- Jag vet att du har upptr&#228;tt f&#246;rut.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:29.958" end="00:06:31.039">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:31.039" end="00:06:32.027">- Som Black Velvet.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:32.027" end="00:06:33.649">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:33.649" end="00:06:34.939">- S&#229; nu upptr&#228;der du som</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34.939" end="00:06:36.666">som Charles Bradley?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:36.666" end="00:06:37.677">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:37.677" end="00:06:38.898">- Du har ett riktigt bra band</p>
      <p begin="00:06:38.898" end="00:06:39.728">bakom dig.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:39.728" end="00:06:41.265">Och sj&#228;lvklart</p>
      <p begin="00:06:41.265" end="00:06:42.898">de som jobbar p&#229; Daptone</p>
      <p begin="00:06:42.898" end="00:06:44.058">jag menar</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.058" end="00:06:44.881">vilken fantastisk grupp de &#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.881" end="00:06:46.190">- Och du har sett vad som</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.190" end="00:06:48.866">h&#228;nde med Sharon Jones, som...<br/>- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:48.866" end="00:06:50.928">som, precis som du</p>
      <p begin="00:06:50.928" end="00:06:52.469">gick fr&#229;n totalt ok&#228;nd till</p>
      <p begin="00:06:52.484" end="00:06:55.048">vem vet hur h&#246;gt du kan n&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:55.048" end="00:06:56.455">- Det &#228;r v&#228;l</p>
      <p begin="00:06:56.455" end="00:06:58.647">en sp&#228;nnande tid f&#246;r dig?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:58.647" end="00:07:01.398">- Jag tror Gud har besvarat mina b&#246;ner</p>
      <p begin="00:07:01.398" end="00:07:03.440">vet du, jag har</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03.440" end="00:07:05.606">fr&#229;gat mig sj&#228;lv varf&#246;r det dr&#246;jde</p>
      <p begin="00:07:05.606" end="00:07:07.023">men du kan inte ifr&#229;gas&#228;tta Gud</p>
      <p begin="00:07:07.023" end="00:07:08.981">n&#228;r han vill g&#246;ra n&#229;gonting.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:08.981" end="00:07:11.915">S&#229; i min &#229;lder b&#246;rjade det h&#228;nda saker.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:11.915" end="00:07:13.482">- Vad &#228;r n&#228;sta steg?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13.482" end="00:07:14.939">Jag menar, har du stora planer?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:14.939" end="00:07:16.706">- Jag t&#228;nker att himlen &#228;r gr&#228;nsen.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:16.706" end="00:07:18.981">- Gratulerar till en fantastisk skiva.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:18.981" end="00:07:20.296">Oavsett vad som h&#228;nder med den</p>
      <p begin="00:07:20.296" end="00:07:22.189">&#228;r den ett riktigt konstverk.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:22.189" end="00:07:24.498">Charles Bradley p&#229; WFUV.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:24.667" end="00:07:27.897"/>
      <p begin="00:07:27.897" end="00:07:33.231">&#9834; V&#228;rlden st&#229;r i brand. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:33.231" end="00:07:38.647">&#9834; Ingen vill ta p&#229; sig ansvaret. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:38.647" end="00:07:43.821">&#9834; S&#228;g inte hur jag ska leva mitt liv. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:43.821" end="00:07:49.276">&#9834; N&#228;r du aldrig k&#228;nt sm&#228;rtan. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:49.276" end="00:07:55.314">&#9834; Ohh. Ahh. Ohh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:55.314" end="00:07:57.856">&#9834; Ohh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:57.856" end="00:08:00.569">&#9834; Ser de inte att jag gr&#229;ter? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:00.569" end="00:08:02.400" region="top"> &#9834; Ohhh... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:02.400" end="00:08:04.315"/>
      <p begin="00:08:04.315" end="00:08:05.564" region="top"> - Jag vet inte hur m&#229;nga artister</p>
      <p begin="00:08:05.564" end="00:08:07.230" region="top"> som varit 62 &#229;r gamla</p>
      <p begin="00:08:07.230" end="00:08:08.955" region="top"> n&#228;r de sl&#228;ppte sin debutskiva.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:09.722" end="00:08:11.458" region="top"> Han kan vara den f&#246;rsta.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:12.284" end="00:08:14.441" region="top"> - Han har bara b&#246;rjat</p>
      <p begin="00:08:14.441" end="00:08:16.440" region="top"> komma ig&#229;ng, s&#229; vitt jag kan se.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:16.440" end="00:08:18.715" region="top"> Han har jobbat h&#229;rt under l&#229;ng tid.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:18.838" end="00:08:20.357" region="top"> Och jag hoppas att</p>
      <p begin="00:08:20.357" end="00:08:21.232" region="top"> tillr&#228;ckligt m&#229;nga <br/>kan h&#246;ra honom sjunga</p>
      <p begin="00:08:21.232" end="00:08:22.647">s&#229; han kan</p>
      <p begin="00:08:22.647" end="00:08:23.856">f&#229; det liv han vill ha</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23.856" end="00:08:25.632">och kunna ta hand om sin familj.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:27.118" end="00:08:30.190">&#9834; Uh. Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:30.190" end="00:08:32.606">&#9834; Jag pratar med dig tjejen. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:32.606" end="00:08:34.023">&#9834; Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:34.023" end="00:08:36.125">&#9834; Bara dig... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:36.125" end="00:08:37.814">- Jag gick till Gabe,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:37.814" end="00:08:39.981">jag t&#228;nkte att han vet vad han g&#246;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:39.981" end="00:08:41.606">Jag k&#228;nde att han kunde hj&#228;lpa mig</p>
