      <p begin="00:19:55.728" end="00:19:58.566">Men inte jag, jag h&#246;ll ett &#246;ga p&#229; dem<br/>medan de sk&#246;t upp</p>
      <p begin="00:19:58.566" end="00:19:59.981">och de f&#246;rs&#246;kte erbjuda mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:59.981" end="00:20:02.340">Men jag blev r&#228;dd, jag gillade inte n&#229;lar.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:02.340" end="00:20:03.815">Jag sa: "Nej, nej, nej."</p>
      <p begin="00:20:03.984" end="00:20:05.814">Det var d&#229; jag gick till Jobs Corps.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:05.937" end="00:20:09.304">Jag f&#246;rs&#246;kte f&#229; mamma att <br/>registrera mig hos Jobs Corps.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:09.411" end="00:20:11.641">Hon var arg p&#229; mig,<br/>s&#229; hon ville inte skriva p&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:11.764" end="00:20:13.872">S&#229; min syster f&#246;rfalskade<br/>hennes namnteckning.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:14.334" end="00:20:15.814">Jag l&#228;rde mig laga mat.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:15.922" end="00:20:17.869">Jag lagade mat i tv&#229; &#229;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:17.992" end="00:20:20.739">Jag var kockl&#228;rling i Bar Harbor, Maine.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:20.739" end="00:20:23.420">Det var d&#229; jag b&#246;rjade g&#246;ra James Brown,<br/>p&#229; Job Corps.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:23.604" end="00:20:26.562">De sa, "Har ni sett den nya killen"?</p>
      <p begin="00:20:26.700" end="00:20:29.924">"Han ser precis ut som James Brown."</p>
      <p begin="00:20:30.998" end="00:20:35.603">Det gjorde mig peppad, de gav mig lite gin<br/>och det var s&#229; p&#229; det jobbet,</p>
      <p begin="00:20:35.603" end="00:20:37.796">man skulle smygdricka.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:38.496" end="00:20:40.932">De gav mig lite gin, jag blev full,</p>
      <p begin="00:20:41.056" end="00:20:43.260">de gav mig en mikrofon och sa: "Sjung."</p>
      <p begin="00:20:43.398" end="00:20:44.575">Och jag sl&#228;ppte loss.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:44.714" end="00:20:47.981">S&#229; de tog mig till <br/>ett Job Corpcenter f&#246;r tjejer</p>
      <p begin="00:20:47.981" end="00:20:50.106">f&#246;r att upptr&#228;da.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:50.106" end="00:20:51.856">Jag fr&#229;gade, "Hur stor &#228;r publiken?"</p>
      <p begin="00:20:51.963" end="00:20:53.423">De sa ungef&#228;r 20 eller 30.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:53.515" end="00:20:54.968">Jag sa "OK".</p>
      <p begin="00:20:55.291" end="00:20:57.836">De bad mig komma upp p&#229; scenen.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:58.143" end="00:20:59.906">Och jag tittade ut &#246;ver scenen.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:00.014" end="00:21:01.474">Jag s&#229;g alla m&#228;nniskor<br/>och jag kunde inte r&#246;ra mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:01.474" end="00:21:02.856">Jag sa:</p>
      <p begin="00:21:02.856" end="00:21:06.856">"Jag v&#228;grar g&#229; ut. Inte jag."</p>
      <p begin="00:21:06.856" end="00:21:11.931">S&#229; en kille som hette Moody<br/>gav mig en knuff.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:12.024" end="00:21:13.485">Jag s&#229;g att alla var glada.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:13.608" end="00:21:14.662">De &#228;lskade mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:14.753" end="00:21:16.620">De &#228;lskade att jag sj&#246;ng fr&#229;n hj&#228;rtat.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:17.050" end="00:21:20.808">Och jag t&#228;nkte:<br/>"Wow, det &#228;r h&#228;r jag h&#246;r hemma."</p>
      <p begin="00:21:20.931" end="00:21:22.559">Jag slutade aldrig efter det.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:25.694" end="00:21:28.613" region="top"> V&#229;r plan n&#228;r vi slutade i Job Corps,</p>
      <p begin="00:21:28.613" end="00:21:30.662" region="top"> var att tr&#228;ffas igen<br/>och forts&#228;tta med musiken.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:30.662" end="00:21:33.909" region="top"> Mitt band blev skickade<br/>till Vietnamkriget.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:33.909" end="00:21:39.781" region="top"> De &#229;kte till kriget och jag gick klart<br/>min tr&#228;ning p&#229; Job Corps.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:46.106" end="00:21:48.189"/>
      <p begin="00:21:48.189" end="00:21:51.514"> </p>
      <p begin="00:21:51.514" end="00:21:55.381">- Jag vill smaka p&#229; den d&#228;r, <br/>n&#228;r du &#246;ppnade s&#229; var det en pumpa.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:55.381" end="00:21:56.778">- Ja, det &#228;r klart.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:56.778" end="00:21:57.977">- Jag m&#229;ste smaka p&#229; det d&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:57.977" end="00:21:59.500">- Vi kan &#246;ppna den nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:59.500" end="00:22:01.232">- Ett pumpa&#246;l, jag har aldrig <br/>h&#246;rt talas om pumpa&#246;l.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:01.232" end="00:22:02.217">- Ja, vi kan dricka lite av det.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:02.217" end="00:22:04.709">- Jag vill verkligen smaka.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:04.805" end="00:22:05.937">- OK.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:07.044" end="00:22:09.108">- Herregud, vad gott!</p>
      <p begin="00:22:09.108" end="00:22:10.799">- Pumpa&#246;l?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:10.799" end="00:22:12.238">- Seri&#246;st, det &#228;r helt otroligt.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:12.238" end="00:22:13.071">- &#196;r det pumpa?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:13.071" end="00:22:13.789">- Yo!</p>
      <p begin="00:22:13.789" end="00:22:14.981">- &#196;r det pumpan?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:14.981" end="00:22:18.882">- Det &#228;r s&#229; det p&#229;verkar vissa m&#228;nniskor.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:18.882" end="00:22:19.974">- Gillar du det nu?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:19.974" end="00:22:21.206">- Nej. - Gillar du det inte?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:21.206" end="00:22:22.231">- Jag gillar det helt enkelt inte.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:22.231" end="00:22:23.419">- Jag tycker det smakar uts&#246;kt.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:23.419" end="00:22:25.763">- Det &#228;r n&#229;gon typ av, pumpasmak d&#228;r i.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:25.948" end="00:22:28.121">- Att jobba med Charles Bradley<br/>&#228;r inte som att jobba med</p>
      <p begin="00:22:28.121" end="00:22:29.731">Sharon Lee eller n&#229;gon av de andra</p>
      <p begin="00:22:29.731" end="00:22:32.884">s&#229;ngarna fr&#229;n New York<br/>som jag ofta jobbar med</p>
      <p begin="00:22:32.884" end="00:22:35.785">Charles har dom galnaste historierna.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:35.981" end="00:22:37.624">De absolut galnaste.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:37.624" end="00:22:41.604">Jag sitter med honom och, <br/>l&#229;tskrivare som jag &#228;r</p>
      <p begin="00:22:41.711" end="00:22:44.372">h&#246;r jag hans historier och t&#228;nker att...</p>
      <p begin="00:22:44.479" end="00:22:47.427">Det d&#228;r m&#229;ste vi g&#246;ra en s&#229;ng av.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:47.427" end="00:22:50.022">S&#229; innan vi spelar in s&#229;ngen till en l&#229;t</p>
      <p begin="00:22:50.022" end="00:22:52.775">s&#228;tter jag p&#229; musiken och</p>
      <p begin="00:22:52.890" end="00:22:53.889">fr&#229;gar Charles om han gillar den.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:53.912" end="00:22:57.171">Sedan sjunger jag mina ide&#233;r f&#246;r honom,<br/>hur jag tycker att det ska vara.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:57.340" end="00:23:00.984">Inte f&#246;r att han avf&#228;rdar mina ide&#233;r,<br/>men han har sina egna</p>
      <p begin="00:23:00.984" end="00:23:04.021">och han b&#246;rjar uttrycka dem direkt.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:04.175" end="00:23:06.664">Han b&#246;rjar sjunga, och sen slutar vi</p>
      <p begin="00:23:06.772" end="00:23:08.540">och b&#246;rjar prata om n&#229;got annat en stund.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:08.540" end="00:23:09.897">- Pratar du med Charles</p>
      <p begin="00:23:09.897" end="00:23:13.940">tillr&#228;ckligt l&#228;nge kommer du att<br/>f&#229; h&#246;ra historier.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:13.940" end="00:23:17.443">Utan att jag fr&#229;gar, s&#229; b&#246;rjar han sjunga</p>
      <p begin="00:23:17.443" end="00:23:19.148">om vad vi pratade om.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:19.148" end="00:23:22.728">Sen h&#228;mtar jag en penna <br/>och l&#229;ter honom improvisera</p>
      <p begin="00:23:22.728" end="00:23:24.481">om och om igen.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:24.481" end="00:23:27.660">- Sen kollar vi igenom det igen<br/>och b&#246;rjar forma det till en s&#229;ng</p>
      <p begin="00:23:27.660" end="00:23:29.297">l&#229;ngsamt, under ett par timmar.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:29.404" end="00:23:32.915">Det &#228;r hans historier jag alltid<br/>f&#246;rs&#246;ker &#246;vers&#228;tta till en s&#229;ng.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:33.038" end="00:23:38.301"/>
      <p begin="00:23:38.455" end="00:23:43.687" region="top"> - Jag &#229;kte till Kalifornien 1977, <br/>jag s&#246;kte mina dr&#246;mmar, musiken.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:44.824" end="00:23:46.897">Jag hoppade mellan olika band.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:46.897" end="00:23:50.763">De sa: "Vi betalar dig 400 dollar<br/>f&#246;r att upptr&#228;da ikv&#228;ll".</p>
      <p begin="00:23:50.870" end="00:23:53.934">Han betalade mig f&#246;r att<br/>upptr&#228;da den kv&#228;llen.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:54.056" end="00:23:55.711">Det var s&#229; det funkade.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:56.050" end="00:24:00.454">Det var d&#229;, vet inte varf&#246;r,<br/>s&#229; blev jag v&#228;ldigt sjuk.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:00.592" end="00:24:05.166">Jag ringde min mamma<br/>och hon sa: "Kom hem."</p>
      <p begin="00:24:07.840" end="00:24:11.200">Mamma b&#246;rjade bli gammal<br/>och hon har varit med om mycket.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:11.292" end="00:24:15.229">Det &#228;r ju inte min uppgift att<br/>anklaga henne f&#246;r hur hon levt sitt liv.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:16.228" end="00:24:20.245" region="top"> S&#229; jag kom tillbaka till New York 1994.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:21.383" end="00:24:24.682" region="top"> Jag var riktigt sjuk, n&#228;ra att d&#246;.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:25.359" end="00:24:27.773" region="top"> De f&#246;rde mig till Woodhulls sjukhus.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:28.173" end="00:24:31.954" region="top"> Jag &#228;r allergisk mot penicillin<br/>och de gav mig penicillin</p>
      <p begin="00:24:32.231" end="00:24:34.758" region="top"> och min kropp st&#228;ngdes av.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:35.880" end="00:24:38.623" region="top"> Jag hade gett upp totalt.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:40.437" end="00:24:48.072">D&#229; kom min bror Joseph<br/>och bes&#246;kte mig p&#229; sjukhuset.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:48.579" end="00:24:51.388">Han b&#246;jde sig ner och pussade mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:51.388" end="00:24:53.483">Han sa "Nej, nej, Charles."</p>
      <p begin="00:24:53.667" end="00:24:55.286">Och han viskade i mitt &#246;ra</p>
      <p begin="00:24:55.471" end="00:25:00.903">Han sa "Min bror, om du inte vill leva <br/>f&#246;r dig sj&#228;lv, lev f&#246;r mig!"</p>
      <p begin="00:25:00.996" end="00:25:02.225">Han sa: "Charles, jag &#228;lskar dig."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:02.670" end="00:25:04.053">"Du &#228;r mitt hj&#228;rta."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:04.314" end="00:25:08.028">Jag sa: "Joe, jag ska k&#228;mpa.<br/>Jag ska k&#228;mpa."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:08.151" end="00:25:14.063"/>
      <p begin="00:25:14.063" end="00:25:18.155">Min bror sa till mig: <br/>"Charles, g&#246;r n&#229;got som du vill g&#246;ra."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:18.599" end="00:25:19.732">"F&#246;lj dina dr&#246;mmar."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:19.732" end="00:25:21.207">"Du &#228;lskar musik, g&#246;r musik."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:21.207" end="00:25:23.004">Och jag sa: "Jag vill vara smart som du."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:23.034" end="00:25:24.772">Han sa: "Nej brorsan, var inte som jag".</p>
      <p begin="00:25:24.895" end="00:25:26.311">"F&#246;rs&#246;k aldrig vara jag. Var dig sj&#228;lv."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:26.449" end="00:25:30.046" region="top"> - Det var hans kompis.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:30.522" end="00:25:32.542" region="top"> Joe gillade, var galen i Charles.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:32.665" end="00:25:36.410" region="top"> Han sa till Charles "Vad du &#228;n g&#246;r,<br/>g&#246;r det bra och forts&#228;tt k&#228;mpa."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:36.517" end="00:25:38.122" region="top"> "L&#229;t inte n&#229;gon prata dig ur det."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:38.429" end="00:25:41.125" region="top"> Det sa han innan han dog.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:41.170" end="00:25:44.809" region="top"> Han sa:<br/>"L&#229;t inte n&#229;gon prata dig ur det."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:44.855" end="00:26:00.797"/>
      <p begin="00:26:00.967" end="00:26:03.075">- Han sa: "Jag kan inte g&#246;ra det som du."</p>
      <p begin="00:26:03.151" end="00:26:05.257">Jag kommer ih&#229;g<br/>n&#228;r jag var liten, i Florida.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:05.441" end="00:26:09.208">Joseph gick p&#229; pianoskola<br/>och l&#228;rde sig alla sm&#229; detaljer,</p>
      <p begin="00:26:09.361" end="00:26:11.442">Jag l&#228;rde mig spela piano,<br/>genom att kolla p&#229; honom.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:12.150" end="00:26:14.901">Han visste aldrig detta - <br/>jag gjorde det sj&#228;lv.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:15.638" end="00:26:18.235">Han sa: "F&#246;lj dina dr&#246;mmar inom musiken"</p>
      <p begin="00:26:18.235" end="00:26:22.413">Han sa: "Ta ett av rummen <br/>och fixa till det"</p>
      <p begin="00:26:22.550" end="00:26:25.656">"G&#246;r det till ditt rum <br/>dit folk kan komma och repa."</p>
      <p begin="00:26:25.779" end="00:26:27.075">Det var det jag gjorde.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:27.581" end="00:26:29.736">Joey var b&#229;de som en pappa och en bror.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:29.829" end="00:26:32.154">Han var en underbar bror.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:32.273" end="00:26:37.726"/>
      <p begin="00:26:37.726" end="00:26:39.212">- Jaha, var &#228;r frukten?</p>
      <p begin="00:26:42.731" end="00:26:46.674"/>
      <p begin="00:26:46.674" end="00:26:48.356">- R&#228;cker det?</p>
      <p begin="00:26:48.356" end="00:26:49.518">- Lite mer.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:49.657" end="00:26:50.985">- Ja, s&#228;tt dig ner Charles, och &#228;t.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:50.985" end="00:26:52.988">- Jag g&#246;r bara lite frukost.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:52.988" end="00:26:54.188">- Jag &#228;r inte hungrig,<br/>det vet du. Men &#228;t du.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:54.326" end="00:26:57.892">Sen b&#246;rjar vi prata om vad du har gjort.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:58.000" end="00:26:59.095">- Okej, jag st&#228;ller den h&#228;r &#229;t dig.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:59.095" end="00:27:00.677">- Det g&#229;r bra.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:00.677" end="00:27:01.924">Jag l&#228;r upp Charles.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:02.047" end="00:27:05.692" region="top"> Jag skulle s&#228;ga att han &#228;r<br/>ungef&#228;r p&#229; dagis- eller f&#246;rstaklassniv&#229;</p>
      <p begin="00:27:05.830" end="00:27:08.303" region="top"> n&#228;r det g&#228;ller l&#228;sf&#246;rst&#229;else.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:08.548" end="00:27:14.017">- &#196;r de intresserade av min story?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:14.017" end="00:27:15.504">- Okej, du gjorde ljuden.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:15.504" end="00:27:17.492">F&#246;rstod du vad du l&#228;ste?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:19.586" end="00:27:23.065">- Hm, ja och nej.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:23.065" end="00:27:24.673">- Ja och nej.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:24.673" end="00:27:25.445">- Charles?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:25.445" end="00:27:26.758">- Hm?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:26.758" end="00:27:28.169" region="top"> - Lunchen var j&#228;ttegod.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:28.277" end="00:27:29.655">- Tack, mamma.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:30.301" end="00:27:35.613">- Jag tror hans fr&#228;msta m&#229;l &#228;r att <br/>kunna skriva sina egna texter snabbt</p>
      <p begin="00:27:35.613" end="00:27:38.419">s&#229; fort de kommer in i hans huvud,</p>
      <p begin="00:27:38.419" end="00:27:41.632">f&#246;r han har m&#229;nga ord i huvudet<br/>som han vill skriva ner p&#229; papper.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:41.740" end="00:27:43.643">Men han vet inte hur man g&#246;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:43.689" end="00:27:44.705">- Du svarade inte "An" r&#228;tt. - OK</p>
      <p begin="00:27:44.705" end="00:27:46.712">- Jaha, tv&#229; N?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:46.712" end="00:27:47.828">- Bara ett N, inget D.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:47.828" end="00:27:49.567">- Jaha, N.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:49.567" end="00:27:52.031">- F&#246;r ordet OCH &#228;r n&#228;r du <br/>pratar om tv&#229; saker som du s&#228;tter ihop..</p>
      <p begin="00:27:52.031" end="00:27:53.656">- Okej, jag f&#246;rst&#229;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:53.656" end="00:27:54.984">- Fish AND chips.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:55.230" end="00:27:56.720">- OK. Jag kommer sakna dig.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:56.890" end="00:27:59.253">- Hejd&#229; Charles. Vi ses n&#228;sta vecka.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:59.421" end="00:28:00.489">Tack.</p>
      <p begin="00:28:00.520" end="00:28:28.550"/>
      <p begin="00:28:28.550" end="00:28:30.698">- Kom in.</p>
      <p begin="00:28:30.785" end="00:28:34.463">- Tar du det? Du kan l&#228;sa senare.<br/>Sluta med det d&#228;r nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:28:34.648" end="00:28:36.289">- Nej. Stick h&#228;r ifr&#229;n. - B&#246;rja jobba.</p>
