      <p begin="01:07:55.753" end="01:07:56.594">- Tre veckor?</p>
      <p begin="01:07:56.634" end="01:07:57.467">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="01:07:57.467" end="01:07:58.829">- Jag kommer sakna dig min son.</p>
      <p begin="01:07:58.829" end="01:08:00.821">- Mm-hm. Du bor h&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:00.943" end="01:08:02.087">Jag kommer ringa dig var tredje dag.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:02.087" end="01:08:04.541">- Okej &#228;lskling.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:09.216" end="01:08:11.334">- Jag &#228;r en bad boy.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:11.473" end="01:08:12.972">Du kan inte ta bort den h&#228;r k&#228;nslan.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:13.388" end="01:08:15.196">Du kan inte ta bort den h&#228;r k&#228;nslan.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:19.091" end="01:08:21.038">- Du kan inte retas. - Jag kan kittla dig.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:23.349" end="01:08:24.756">Jag kan kittla dig.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:24.756" end="01:08:35.407"/>
      <p begin="01:08:35.591" end="01:08:37.695">Som min mamma sa idag</p>
      <p begin="01:08:38.017" end="01:08:46.239">hon trodde aldrig att jag skulle <br/>ta mig till den h&#228;r niv&#229;n.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:46.319" end="01:08:57.718"/>
      <p begin="01:08:57.778" end="01:09:02.683">Jag vill se hur l&#229;ngt <br/>jag kan ta mig i livet.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:03.789" end="01:09:09.016">Se om jag kan ta mig l&#228;ngre <br/>&#228;n alla mina familjemedlemmar.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:09.431" end="01:09:11.976">Och du ser, det tog mig hit.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:13.283" end="01:09:15.306">Alla d&#228;r ute, se upp.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:15.429" end="01:09:18.713">En gammal man &#228;r p&#229; v&#228;g<br/>och jag g&#246;r ert jobb b&#228;ttre &#228;n ni.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:18.896" end="01:09:23.704">Om inte, g&#246;r jag det &#229;t er.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:27.514" end="01:09:59.318"/>
      <p begin="01:10:17.932" end="01:10:19.785">- Vill du jobba p&#229; den<br/>d&#228;r l&#229;ten fr&#229;n f&#246;rra veckan?</p>
      <p begin="01:10:19.923" end="01:10:21.003">- Vilken?</p>
      <p begin="01:10:21.141" end="01:10:22.635">- I Thank You (Jag tackar dig).</p>
      <p begin="01:10:22.759" end="01:10:48.002"/>
      <p begin="01:10:48.141" end="01:10:50.704">- Han b&#246;rjar verkligen bli bra.</p>
      <p begin="01:10:50.826" end="01:10:59.981"/>
      <p begin="01:10:59.981" end="01:11:02.794">Ahh!</p>
      <p begin="01:11:02.794" end="01:11:08.526">S&#229;dan &#228;r jag.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:08.526" end="01:11:17.204"/>
      <p begin="01:11:17.454" end="01:11:19.988">Woo.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:52.578" end="01:11:55.763">- N&#228;r jag l&#228;mnar den h&#228;r v&#228;rlden <br/>&#228;r v&#228;rlden inte skyldig mig n&#229;got.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:55.902" end="01:11:57.423">- Ge mig tillbaks min dollar nu.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:00.067" end="01:12:01.636">- L&#228;gg av.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:01.762" end="01:12:03.463">- Ge mig tillbaks min dollar.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:04.481" end="01:12:13.267"/>
      <p begin="01:12:13.267" end="01:12:14.327">- Mitt pass, v&#228;nta lite.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:14.465" end="01:12:35.156"/>
      <p begin="01:12:35.295" end="01:12:37.234">- Spara din hummer.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:38.863" end="01:12:41.744">- Jimmy, du &#228;ter inte hummer, <br/>du ger den alltid till mig.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:41.913" end="01:12:43.208">- Jag ska b&#246;rja &#228;ta det idag.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:43.423" end="01:13:05.159"/>
      <p begin="01:13:05.406" end="01:13:09.310">- Du &#228;r verkligen snabb, <br/>det &#228;r min quarter. Jag s&#229;g det.</p>
      <p begin="01:13:09.417" end="01:13:10.692">- Jag plockade upp den.</p>
      <p begin="01:13:10.872" end="01:14:14.421"/>
